'''Headup GmbH''' is a German [[video game publisher]] based in [[Düren]]. The company was founded in January 2009 by Dieter Schoeller, who currently serves as the company's [[managing director]]. In 2012, 2013 and 2017, Headup Games won the "Bester Publisher" ("Best Publisher") award at the {{Interlanguage link|Deutscher Entwicklerpreis|de}} award show.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deutscherentwicklerpreis.de/preistraeger?field_jahr_tid=29 |title=Preisträger Chronologie: 2012 |trans-title=Prize Winners Chronology: 2012 |website=[[Deutscher Entwicklerpreis]] |language=de |accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://deutscherentwicklerpreis.de/preistraeger?field_jahr_tid=28 |title=Preisträger Chronologie: 2013 |trans-title=Prize Winners Chronology: 2013 |website=[[Deutscher Entwicklerpreis]] |language=de |accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://deutscherentwicklerpreis.de/preistraeger?field_jahr_tid=171 |title=Preisträger Chronologie: 2017 |trans-title=Prize Winners Chronology: 2017 |website=[[Deutscher Entwicklerpreis]] |language=de |accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref> The company is best known for publishing the ''[[Bridge Constructor]]'' series of games, developed by [[ClockStone]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/311145/Valve_licenses_Portal_to_Headup_for_new_Bridge_Constructor_game.php |title=Valve licenses ''Portal'' to Headup for new ''Bridge Constructor'' game |first=Emma |last=Kidwell |date=6 December 2017 |website=[[Gamasutra]] |accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>

